00:18:49,766 --> 00:18:54,247
you look at an Assassin's Creed Odyssey, you look at a Red Dead Redemption two,

256
00:18:54,247 --> 00:18:58,248
you know, these are massive living worlds that players want to be immersed in.

257
00:18:58,248 --> 00:19:00,528
And for us, immersion is another keyword

258
00:19:00,528 --> 00:19:03,609
that we really established very early on in the program.

259
00:19:03,609 --> 00:19:07,430
It's like, how can we keep players really immersed in the universes

