00:19:28,965 --> 00:19:35,131
So, you know, compatibility was another key pillar that we established very early in the program

266
00:19:35,131 --> 00:19:39,935
because, as I've said before, you know, there's no other medium, whether it's movies or music

267
00:19:39,935 --> 00:19:45,841
or books, that when I go out and buy a new device that my content doesn't move forward with me.

268
00:19:45,841 --> 00:19:50,726
