00:19:51,627 --> 00:19:55,489
So we actually considered that when we designed the hardware.

270
00:19:55,489 --> 00:20:01,633
And one of the things that we're really proud of is that when games are running on the Xbox Series X and Series S,

271
00:20:01,633 --> 00:20:06,776
