00:20:38,446 --> 00:20:42,790
the game doesn't feel the same or doesn't look the same or you get visual artifacts.

281
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:47,995
And the only way that we can achieve that is through a tremendous amount of testing

282
00:20:47,995 --> 00:20:50,577
that we do across the entire catalog of games.

283
00:20:51,097 --> 00:20:56,042
And I think it just really comes down to, you know, for us, a real player-centric approach,

